snippet.title: Invite The Blackbird game trailer
snippet.description:
Invite The Blackbird is a hand-drawn watercolour 2d game made in a form of comics. 
Play for free here: https://anamerzlaya.itch.io/invite-the-blackbird
Follow the heart-warming story about Sonya and the blackbird. As the story unfolds, few point-and-click puzzles will be on your way.
